# Touch this file to fire .github/workflows/notion-brochure-db.yml
# (push trigger). The workflow runs setup-schema + push-turkey
# sequentially when this file changes. Idempotent on both ends.
#
# v1 — initial Turkey populate
# v2 — switch to human-friendly Notion names with circled-digit section icons, rename Name → alias
# v3 — generalised extract for all 12 brochures, flag-prefixed alias, per-country Notion page cover
# v4 — preserve inline <strong>/<em>/<a href> in prose fields (extract via prose_html); stop escaping in render
# v5 — repopulate all 12 rows (11 programs beyond turkey were missing from Notion DB)
# v6 — extractor fixes: hero_bg_img (CSS + inline), nac_score_label (.star-label
#      fallback), info-box class variants (green/amber/gold), fam-card without
#      inner div wrapper, breadcrumb in <nav> or <div>, s09 fallback to
#      nac-box <p> when no info-box. Improves VI field coverage from ~9 gap
#      fields to 7 (the rest are genuine HTML omissions per-brochure).
